name: NEW! Palmer River Roadhouse Belt
description: This versatile pocket belt is made from 100% organic cotton.  It features two removable pockets on each side.  It can be worn with or without pockets or with just one.  The triangular sections holding the brass rings also have secret velcro pockets.  The corset lacing on the back makes the belt adjustable to many different body types and sizes.  The snaps can also be adjusted to size.

name: NEW! Voom Vest
description: This 97% organic cotton/3% spandex vest can be worn layered over a tank top or on it's own.  It's short length works well with high waist clothing.  It has interior snaps which allows it to fit well over the bust as well as two snaps on the shoulder to hold it all in place.  It can also be worn open and has strategically positioned snaps that allow the vest to stay in place in a loose fitting manner when open.

name: NEW! Strawberry Dress
description: This sexy fun dress is made from 90% organic cotton and 10% spandex.  It features an asymmetrical tutu-esque skirt with a varying colour underneath.  The straps are adjustable with a simple tie.  It has a racerback cut.  It is very flattering for all shapes and sizes!

name: NEW! Terri Vest
description: This vest comes in many colour combos and goes well with high waist bottoms as well as looks amazing when layered over tanks, tees or fitted long sleeve tops.  It is made from 100% organic cotton.

name: NEW! High Waist Shorties
description: These sexy yet tasteful shorts are made from 97% organic cotton and 3% spandex.  They usually sit right above the belly button and work well with short tops or tight tops that can be tucked in.  The heavy duty snaps give a stylish edge and make them a great fit.  They have back pockets.

name: NEW! Lacey Star Halter Top
description: This top is made from 90% organic cotton and 10% Lycra.  It has an adjustable neck as well as the lacing on the back can be adjusted to any specific size.  There is also another tie just above the lacing that provides extra support for the bust.  There are brass loops at the front and the back for a stylish edge.

name: NEW! Frillz Half Top
description: This top is perfect for wearing with high waist bottoms or if you feel that constant longing for the early 90's ;)  It comes in our comfy and fitted 90% organic cotton/10% spandex fabric.

name: NEW! Frillz Top
description: This top is made from 90% organic cotton and 10% spandex.  It has a tasteful frill along the collar which dips over one shoulder.  The tight band at the bottom can be worn high or low for a loose or fitted effect.

name: NEW! Juliet Jumper
description: This comfy and slinky long sleeve hoodie is fitted and features an empire waist.  It has lots of extra fabric around the shoulders resembling a shawl.

name: NEW! Wing Skirt
description: This skirt is made from 90% organic cotton and 10% spandex.  It can be worn up high or very low on the hips.  It features patterned buttons along the front (with 2 extra in case you lose any :) and ruching on the bum for a bustle look.

name: NEW! Folk Frill Skirt
description: This skirt is made from 97% organic cotton and 3% spandex.  It can be worn high or low on the hips.  It has pockets on either side and can be cinched up in the front.  The back resembles a bustle :)

name: NEW! Terri Hoodie
description: This cozy stylish hoodie is made from 100% organic cotton.  It has three buttons above the zipper to gather up the collar.  It is long for extra bum coziness :)

name: NEW! Genie Pants
description: These drop crotch pants can be worn up high or low on the hips.  They are made from our 97% organic cotton/3% lycra fabric.  They are unisex and can be adjusted using the corset lacing at the waist as well as at the ankles.

name: NEW! Low Crotch Sailor Pants
description: These pants are made with 100% organic cotton canvas.  They feature a snap up flap at the front as well as belt loops.  There have deep side pockets that start about half way down the pants.  They have a tapered leg cut so they fit well with boots and sneakers.

name: NEW! Guy's Lattice Shorts
description: These heavy duty 100% Organic Cotton canvas shorts are perfect for a summer romp or just standing in front of a wall looking ultra stylish like this guy ;)  They offer lots of pockets including unique deep pockets along the bottom of the shorts.

name: NEW! Bass Torn Singlet
description: This guy's singlet/muscle shirt/tank has one of two Rabbit & Empee custom designed prints by Mugwort.  It is made from 100% organic cotton.

name: NEW! Guys Bass Torn Tshirt
description: This Tshirt style features 2 different Mugwort prints custom made for Rabbit & Empee.  It has rips on the shoulders and shoulder blades with a different colour fabric showing through.  It is made from 100% organic cotton.

name: NEW! Sailor Jacket
description: This durable medium weight 100% organic cotton canvas jacket is lined with 100% organic cotton french terri.  It has snaps along the front as well as a zipper under the panels.  It has a pocket watch/wallet chain built into the side pocket.  The collar can be snapped down.  The french terri protrudes from the sleeves making it longer and giving it that comfy rugged look.

name: NEW! Flight Jacket
description: This Rabbit and Empee style bomber jacket is made from 100% organic cotton canvas.  It features a diagonal zipper with snaps that button the collar all the way up starting mid-jacket.  The side pockets have a big hole for your hands and a smaller section that snaps shut for all your bits and bobs :)  It also has an awesome size hood.

name: NEW! Let Ur Fly Down Pants
description: These pants allow you to forget to zip up your fly sometimes since it offers a practical front zipper cover ;)  Adorned with metal studs these light weight pants have acid washed panels and are made from 97% organic cotton/3% spandex.  There are deep back pockets and look good straight leg or rolled up.

name: Guy's Organic French Terri Hoodie
description: Cozy and sexy organic french terri hoodie...Print design by Danielle Helen Ray Dickson

name: Bikini Top
description:
Bass Torn Bikini top matches the Bass Torn 
Tights or Booty Shorts completing the set.

name: Butterfly Top
description: This summery top is made from 90% organic cotton/10% spandex and has an adjustable back for extra support and size versatility.  It can be worn with a tube top underneath as well for extra coverage.  There are hidden pockets underneath the triangular front flaps.

name: Scallywag Singlet
description: Comfortable and supportive organic cotton stretch jersey singlet. Lots of cool design aspects and subtle details making an original out of a classic cut.

name: Bolero Top
description: Organic Cotton Stretch Jersey. This sleeveless top is full of support and comfort, with a slice of sexiness, showing the upper back. Comes in a large variety of colours.

name: Salsa skirt
description: Made with Organic Cotton Stretch Jersey, a light material perfect from summer. Wear it long or hike it up with the help of handy ties located on either side of the skirt.

name: Princess Dress
description: Made from 90% organic cotton/10% spandex this top can be used as a top or short dress.  The festive detail includes long pixie hood and short sleeves that leave your shoulders exposed to reflect moonbeams whilst grooving on forest dance floors! The comfy cotton is form fitting, super soft, and extremely durable.  This is one of our most popular items at festivals and in town.

name: Zen Komono Top
description: Simple, minimal, elegant, natural.  Crafted from organic stretch jersey, the Komono Top can be worn as a top with tights or pants, or even as a short skirt for hot summer days.

name: West End Overcoat
description: The WEO combines three types of Orgainc fabrics, giving it durability, flexability, and soft cozy warmth for fall and spring, or cool Canadian summer nights. The adjustable corset style back flatters all body types giving it a shapely form. Hand warmers can be worn or simply tucked away. All of our hardware has been updated with higher quality snaps and studs this year so go hard and do what you will with this new classic!

name: Samurai Vest (Lined with cozy Micro-Terri)
description: Stretch  organic cotton canvas shell, lined with soft cozy organic terri, the Samari Vest is perfect for spring and fall days, and cool summer nights. Its Stretch compliments all body types adding curves, while remaining comfortable. The hood zips off for a smarter dynamic look. Big pockets for wallets, keys or you hands.

name: Arabic Geometry Tube Dress
description: This simple edgy design combines both soft organic stretch jersey with an light organics stretchy poplin, stylishly printed with our signature geometric pattern. Add our Booty Shorts and feel free kickin it anywhere you want!

name: Landsdowne Trousers
description: Don't let these tight fitting trousers stop your active lifestyle! Made with streeeeetchy organic cotton canvas, the Landsdowne feel like an extra skin. Styled with ruching, and a very complimentary sexy waistline adding a feminine flare, balanced by sailor style snaps in the front, and heavy brass waist adjusters adding that edge of attitude.

name: Cowboyz Shirt
description: 100% Organic Cotton Jersey long sleeve men's shirt with an arabic geometry pattern.  Detailed with engraved brass buttons and textured with outside seams giving it a subtle raw  outlandish feel.

name: Guys 1.618 Shorts
description: Fitted, yet still loose enough to jump around and be active. These 3/4 shorts are made with streeeeeetch organic cotton canvas, which feels just like and extra layer of skin. The design is off the hook with angled bottoms, textured external stitching, subtle Arabic Geometric prints, and probably too much pocket space!. We've stepped up the hardware this year as well adding super tough engraved brass snaps and studs.

name: Armadillo Terri Lined Vest
description: This organic canvas men's hooded vest is lined with Terri(think of your favorite hoodie material) and is perfect for spring and chilly summer festival nights.  Well equipped with two secret zippered pockets in the armadillo layers of the hood.  There are also two pockets at the front. One with a snap and another with a zipper, for extra security.  Located at the bottom sides are zippers allowing for an extra little space of comfort if needed.

name: Armadillo Vest
description: This organic canvas men's hooded vest is perfect for anytime of the year.  Well equipped with two secret zippered pockets in the armadillo layers of the hood.  There are also two pockets at the front. One with a snap and another with a zipper, for extra security.  Located at the bottom sides are zippers allowing for an extra little space of comfort if needed.

name: Desert Hoodie
description: This top features a loose cowel neck that can also be worn as a hood.  Reminiscent of a desert gypsy princess this top also has some modern useful features such as a big double sided pocket in the front.  It also has lacing with brass eyelets on the bottom of each side so the base of the top can be adjusted to suit/mask the belly.  The back arches down a little being a few centimetres longer than the front.  The sleeves have some accentuating folded detail.

name: Kali Valley Vest
description: This vest is made from organic cotton canvas and has fleece lining.  It has 2 pockets at the front and corset style lacing at the back to make it adjustable for any shape.  The measurement for the Small Kali Vest is 32 inches across the chest and the waist has an adjustable corset in the back allowing the size to range from 26 to 34 inches.  The next size up is 2 inches bigger and so on for the other sizes.

name: Halter Tee Hoodie
description: This top is a revamped edition of the Halter Tee Top.  The 3/4 length sleeves are a little folded for a defined shoulder.  There are two ties in the back: one that offers support for the chest and the other covers the belly and can be worn more loosely to mask any sort of bellyness.

name: Halter Tee Top
description:
The Halter Tee Top is an adjustable 'tee'. Sexy low neck line and open back are perfect cuts for warm summer days and nights. It is adjustable around the bust and tummy.  Made from soft organic cotton lycra.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Halter Vest
description: This halter vest has been revamped since last year!  It can be worn over a top or simply by itself.  It is made from 3% Lycra and 97% Organic Cotton canvas and has 2 ties at the back making the sizing very versatile.  There are small pockets on either side and brass buttons.  The back of the collar is pointed which can be worn flipped up or down and there is vegan suede piping outlining the vest.

name: Ribbed Halter Combination
description:
Organic cotton lycra adjustable cowl neck with supportive inner layer, which has a textured detail design sewn into it. This top is very adjustable with 3 ties in the back. The material is super comfy, soft, and form fitting.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Bass Torn Booty Shorts
description: Made from 92% Organic Cotton and 8% Lycra these cute booty shorts can be worn under skirts, to the beach or anywhere you please...The torn style is outlined by a matching tattered frill.

name: Bubble Bottom Pantalones
description: Sailor style capri pants with adjustable lacing on the back accommodating multiple waist sizes. These pants fit all booties like a glove! Made with 3% lycra and 97% organic cotton canvas, these pants are sure to form around all your curves. Have fun adjusting the billowing bubbles at the bottom to suit tall boots, or bare feet. "Arrrrrrr me lass!" Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions. Click Here to view pics of various shapes, sizes & sexes sporting R & E's most popular item on our blog

name: Bass Torn Tights
description: Super durable leggings made form 92% organic cotton and 8 % lycra.  Flexible and funky, these leggings are great for all seasons.  You can wear them as pants or under skirts and dresses.  They have a thick waist band with secret a pocket and are one size fits most.

name: Lotus Skirt
description: Inspired from the Lotus flower, this skirt has a thick bannd and adjustable sides for added comfort.  It is made from and Organic Cotton Lycra blend.

name: Shkirt
description:
Organic cotton/lycra skirt, that is also designed to be worn as a top. It comes in two sizes and easily accommodates all sizes because of its stretchy nature.
Email rabbitanvil@gmail with any questions.

name: Optikoppler
description:
Made from very soft organic cotton canvas, with 3% lycra, this long sleeve bolero style jacket is very form fitting. The Optikoppler attaches above the chest by means of 2 laces. The sleeve ends, and hood have lacing for detail. Other detail includes fraying edges, brass studs, and monochromatic two tone colouring. 
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Bustle Belt
description: Ruffle bustle pocketed for massive cargo! Redefining the phrase "Junk in the Trunk!" Big it up ladies this summer with antiquated modernity.

name: Pushkar Belt
description: This sturdy organic cotton canvas belt features one large pocket with two smaller pockets on the front.  It has a series of adjustable buttons that can be adjusted from 29'' to 41" for varying waist sizes.

name: Mandala Belt
description: This sturdy organic cotton hip sack features a large double pocket both with zippers and snaps for extra security.  There are 2 smaller pockets on either side of the larger centre pocket.  There is also a hidden zipper on the inside of the belt.  There is stitching detail on the top flap of all the pockets as well as piping outlining each pocket.  There are a series of eight eyelets in between each pocket for an industrial urban look.  The waist/hip size can be adjusted from 32 to 45 inches.

name: Armadillo Pouch
description:
The Armadillo Pouch is the perfect utility belt for those who really love to stay organized.  This tough organic canvas belt boasts 6 pockets, 3 of which are attached to the largest side pocket. Rabbit designed this handy Porto-Pocket after the exoskeleton-like shell of the armadillo.  This year we've added faux-suede piping around the edges to accentuate the flaps.  Rogues love this one!
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Phangan Pouch
description:
This hipsack was conceived at an outdoor party in Thailand's Koh Phangan Island.  It is our most popular single pouch hipsack.  Super tough, comes with 2 security zippers, and multi organizational pockets inside the large main pouch which is easily large enough to accommodate a camera, fat wallet and tobacco pouch.  Machine washable. Easily adjusts to all sizes with multiple tough security snaps.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Sailor Belt
description: This sailor style belt 100% organic cotton belt can be adjusted using the corset in the back.  Once the size is set, the four buttons in the front can be used to take the belt on and off.  There are 2 large pockets and 2 small pockets as well as a hidden zipper pocket on the inside of the belt.

name: Goa Belt
description:
Organic Canvas multi-pocket party utility belt. Modeled after a classic Goa style leather design, but now in Vegan friendly Canvas!
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Tool Belt
description:
The tool belt is the perfect utility belt for day outings, festivals, or around the studio. It comes with 4 spacious cargo style pockets that extend easily an inch and a half, and tuck away nicely when not very full. 2 secure zippered safety pockets line the inside close to your body. Constructed from super durable organic cotton canvas, attaches with tough bras snaps.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com with any questions.

name: Leaf Pouch
description:
Multi pocket utility belt with adjustable corset style back. Each zippered pocket is covered by a hanging leaf!  Made with super durable orgainc cotton.  This belt is extremely adjustable and can accommodate sizes both larger and smaller than the waist sizes listed.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Point Pocket
description:
This organic canvas Porto-Pocket is our sleekest gal's model, which attaches using a belt buckle rather than snaps, giving it a more formal look. This small casual pocket works well with jeans or skirts. It has 2 tiny secret pockets on either side of the point.  Its pointy pocket easily accommodates a thin wallet, cell phone, and keys or perhaps just a card, making it the perfect accessory for a night on the town. 
Please feel free to email us if you have any questions rabbitanvil@gmail.com

name: Bubble Shorts
description:
Organic cotton Lycra canvas shorts, which can be word both short and long. The front is inspired by old sailor style pants, but uses industrial snaps instead of buttons. The back laces up accommodating waist sizes for a custom fit. The stretch canvas is as soft and comfy as the lycra, only more durable for active wear.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: Storm Rider Pants
description: These sturdy 100% organic cotton canvas pants feature double zippers on both sides and are loosely fitted.  They have an assortment of pockets outlined by piping.

name: Rogues 3/4 Shorts
description: 3/4 length tough canvas shorts with deep back pockets including a huge sideways pocket at the very bottom of the leg.  Subtle armadillo detailing at the sides.

name: Lace-Up Pixie Hoodie
description:
Cowl neck sleeveless hoodie with comfortable and beautiful open back. This piece blends medieval lace corset with pixie sass and urban sophistication. As with all of our line, it is equitably made with certified organic cotton.
Please email rabbitanvil@gmail.com if you have any questions.

name: High Top Sandal Boots
description: A variation on last season's sandal boots with double the height reaching to the calf.  They have 5 snaps in the back which can be worn all the way up or half undone emphasizing the differing colour on the inside.  They feature frayed seams and an arabic geometry print.

name: Sandal Boots
description: Made from 100% organic cotton these durable Sandal Boots feature an arabic geometric print.

name: Bone Seagull
description: Seagull skull or head hand carved from water buffalo bone.  Our plugs and stretchers are ethically hand made by our friend Wayan in Bali, Indonesia who we've been working with for over 5 years.  We work directly with the producer and all money goes directly to him and his family.   The bone is collected from expired water buffalos which are used for plowing rice fields and other farm related activities in Indonesia.

name: Mini Bass Torn Arm Warmers
description: Two-toned ripped gloves made from 92% organic cotton and 8% lycra.  A perfect addition to a party outfit or a colourful way to spice up the season!  Available in One Size only

name: Full Length Bass Torn Arm Warmers
description: These ful length fingerless sleeves are a great accessory that can be paired with a variety of tanks and tees :)

name: Leg Warmers
description: Organic cotton jersey leg warmers that adjust with lacing and sit above the calf. One size fits all.
